Pizza Delivery App (Full-Stack Experience)
A modern, high-performance pizza ordering application built with a focus on seamless user experience, complex state management, and localized content.

Live Demo: https://pizza-shop-mu-five.vercel.app/login

Key Features Multilingual Support: Dynamic language switching for a global user experience.

Advanced Filtering & Sorting: Users can sort items by price, popularity, or name.

Real-time Search: Instant pizza lookup functionality using efficient filtering logic.

Authentication System: Secure user login to access personalized ordering features.

Smart Shopping Cart: Full state control (Add/Remove/Update) using Redux Toolkit.

Responsive UX: Fully optimized for mobile, tablet, and desktop screens.

Tech Stack Frontend: React 18

Type Safety: TypeScript

State Management: Redux Toolkit (@reduxjs/toolkit)

Routing: React Router 6

Styling: Tailwind CSS

Deployment: Vercel
